15:T431,
## Welcome

This documentation helps **HR managers**, **recruiters**, and **admins** get the most out of HR — the all-in-one HR platform for Bulgarian businesses.

## What you'll find here

- **[Getting Started](/docs/getting-started)** — Set up your account, invite your team, and run your first workflows.
- **[Features](/docs/features)** — Deep dives into Core HR, ATS, Leave, Payroll, Performance, and Onboarding.
- **[Core Concepts](/docs/core-concepts)** — Architecture, multi-tenancy, and technology stack.
- **[SDK & API Guides](/docs/sdk-guides)** — REST API integration, authentication, and curl examples.

## Quick links

| I want to… | Go to |
|------------|--------|
| Post my first job | [Quickstart](/docs/getting-started/quickstart) |
| Configure leave types | [Leave Management](/docs/features/leave) |
| Run payroll (Bulgaria) | [Payroll](/docs/features/payroll) |
| Set up AI CV screening | [ATS & Recruitment](/docs/features/ats) |

Need help? Visit the [Help Center](https://hr.bg/help-center) or [contact support](https://hr.bg/contact).
